@title Pausable
 @dev Base contract which allows children contracts to implement emergency stop.
@dev Modifier to make a function callable only when the contract is not paused.
@dev Modifier to make a function callable only when the contract is paused.
@dev called only by the owner to pause, triggers stopped state

@dev called only by the owner to unpause,
 returns to normal state
